cross.datastructures.fragments
Class ImmutableFileFragment

java.lang.Object
  cross.datastructures.fragments.ImmutableFileFragment
All Implemented Interfaces:
IFileFragment, IFragment, IGroupFragment, IIterableFragment, IXMLSerializable, java.io.Externalizable, java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<java.lang.Object>, java.lang.Iterable<IVariableFragment>, java.util.Comparator<IFragment>
public class ImmutableFileFragment
extends java.lang.Object
implements IFileFragment

Immutable Variant of a FileFragment. All set operations will throw UnsupportedOperationException. All other operations delegate to an instance of IFileFragment, which is provided to the constructor.

Author:
Nils.Hoffmann@CeBiTec.Uni-Bielefeld.DE
